title: With 240 SME IPOs giving an average return of about 86% in 2024, ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund's CIO
author: ETMarkets
description:
With 240 SME IPOs giving an average return of about 86% in 2024, ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund's CIO S Naren has warned retail investors against venturing in what he calls the most dangerous part of the market.
